OL,3,CHighways deserted and tensions high as
OL,4,Cpeople flee southern Lebanon
OL,6,FHezbollah is ready for a long battle
OL,7,Fwith Israel, as ITV News Correspondent
OL,8,FJohn Ray reports from southern Lebanon
OL,10,FWe are about ten miles from the
OL,11,FLebanese border with Israel ` and
OL,12,Fsince we arrived we have heard the
OL,13,Fconstant thump of explosions on the
OL,14,Fhillside ahead of us and watched the
OL,15,Frising plume of smoke that followed.
OL,17,FIsrael has warned civilians in two
OL,18,Fdozen villages to leave their homes,
OL,19,Fas it targets what it takes to
OL,20,FHezbollah positions concealed there.
