OL,3,CHighways deserted and tensions high as
OL,4,Cpeople flee southern Lebanon
OL,6,FLocal health officials say five people
OL,7,Fhave been killed and nine wounded this
OL,8,Fmorning alone.
OL,10,FThe drive south from the capital was
OL,11,Falong an almost deserted highway.
OL,12,FIsrael says they consider any car a
OL,13,Fpotential target as they may be
OL,14,Fcarrying Hezbollah fighters.
OL,16,FThe only soldiers we saw were from the
OL,17,FLebanese Army ` who had been ordered
OL,18,Fto leave their positions. This is not
OL,19,Ftheir war.
