OL,3,CHighways deserted and tensions high as
OL,4,Cpeople flee southern Lebanon
OL,6,FIn the seaside town of Tyre, almost
OL,7,Fevery shop and business is closed. The
OL,8,Fatmosphere is tense. Many here have
OL,9,Flived through previous Israeli
OL,10,Finvasions.
OL,12,FThis time, Israel calls Operation
OL,13,FNorthern Arrows "limited" and
OL,14,F"targeted".
OL,16,FBut wars have a momentum of their own.
OL,17,FThey can confound the best-laid plans.
